Yes, actually it is a mass market and good place for product recognition.

: Does this mean ALL VIScorp products (like, say, oh, I don't know,
: AMIGAS maybe) will be sold at Kmart? 

Viscorp's setop it seems will be from reading your quoted article, but 
alas, no mention of selling any Amiga :(

I say alas, because Amiga sales at Kmart would sure give the Amiga the 
publicity it could use, and a "household" Amiga at Kmart will survive.

: I dunno if this is such a great idea. I argued against this tooth
