Yes, but again, the Amiga needs the boost in sales. No sales=No more Amigas.

: Well hey, it's great exposure at the very least. I've been seeing
: things about VIScorp all over the place, on TV, in the papers, etc. and they
: all mention the Amiga!

Yeah!! just my point.

